# 📊 Financial Statement Analysis of TCS (Python Project)

## 📌 Overview

This project performs financial statement analysis of Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) using Python.
It evaluates the company’s performance using key financial ratios and visualizations.

---

## 🎯 Objective

* Analyze financial performance using real company data
* Calculate financial ratios
* Visualize trends
* Generate insights

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used

* Python
* Pandas
* Matplotlib

---

## 📂 Project Structure

data/ → financial data
src/ → Python code
output/ → charts

---

## 📊 Key Metrics

* Revenue Growth
* Profit Margin
* ROE (Return on Equity)
* ROA (Return on Assets)
* Debt to Equity
* Asset Turnover

